When I run the showoci.py script it is unable to get DB info for the one DB we have that is in a dataguard relationship.

Error in ShowOCIService:__load_database_dbsystems: {'opc-request-id': '46DDE89FBF1B45158329B6EB3171CE30/4807B228DCEBF3E66664AE64C26894ED/B175E746E22E35FBF7F12F661615DFDA', 'code': 'InvalidParameter', 'message': 'Expected region phx but found region iad', 'status': 400}

I'm not sure if it's because the DBs have the same name or the fact that there is a dataguard relationship.

